%% SAS Token Generation and File Upload Flow
%% Detailed sequence showing User Delegation SAS pattern

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as ðŸ‘¤ User
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant API as Fastify API
    participant Identity as Managed Identity
    participant Entra as Microsoft Entra ID
    participant Storage as Azure Blob Storage
    
    %% File Selection
    User->>Frontend: 1. Click "SELECT FILE" button
    Frontend->>Frontend: File selected (photo.jpg)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Validate file size (< 256KB)
    
    %% SAS Token Request
    User->>Frontend: 2. Click "GET SAS TOKEN" button
    Note over Frontend,API: Phase 1: Request SAS Token
    Frontend->>API: 3. GET /api/sas?file=photo.jpg<br/>&container=upload&permission=w<br/>&timerange=10
    
    %% CORS Preflight
    Note over API: Check CORS origin
    API-->>Frontend: OPTIONS 200 (CORS OK)
    
    %% Authentication Flow
    Note over API,Entra: Phase 2: Authenticate with Azure
    API->>Identity: 4. Get credential<br/>(DefaultAzureCredential)
    Identity->>Entra: 5. Request OAuth token<br/>(using Managed Identity)
    Entra->>Entra: Validate identity
    Entra-->>Identity: 6. Return access token
    Identity-->>API: 7. Return credential
    
    %% User Delegation Key Request
    Note over API,Storage: Phase 3: Get User Delegation Key
    API->>Storage: 8. getUserDelegationKey()<br/>startsOn: now<br/>expiresOn: now+10min
    Storage->>Entra: 9. Validate token & RBAC<br/>(Storage Blob Delegator)
    Entra-->>Storage: 10. Authorization granted
    Storage-->>API: 11. Return User Delegation Key<br/>(temporary signing key)
    
    %% SAS Token Generation
    Note over API: Phase 4: Generate SAS Token
    API->>API: 12. generateBlobSASQueryParameters()<br/>- containerName: upload<br/>- blobName: photo.jpg<br/>- permissions: write<br/>- startsOn, expiresOn<br/>- userDelegationKey
    API->>API: 13. HMAC-SHA256 signature<br/>with user delegation key
    API->>API: 14. Construct SAS URL:<br/>https://{account}.blob.core.windows.net<br/>/upload/photo.jpg?sv=...&sig=...
    
    %% Return SAS to Frontend
    API-->>Frontend: 15. Return JSON:<br/>{ "url": "https://...?{sas-params}" }
    Frontend->>Frontend: 16. Store SAS URL in state
    
    %% File Upload
    Note over Frontend,Storage: Phase 5: Upload File Directly to Storage
    User->>Frontend: 17. Click "UPLOAD FILE" button
    Frontend->>Frontend: 18. Convert File to ArrayBuffer
    Frontend->>Storage: 19. PUT /upload/photo.jpg<br/>with SAS query params<br/>Body: file data
    
    %% SAS Validation
    Storage->>Storage: 20. Validate SAS:<br/>- Signature matches?<br/>- Not expired?<br/>- Permission = write?
    Storage->>Entra: 21. Verify user delegation key<br/>still valid
    Entra-->>Storage: 22. Key valid
    
    %% Store File
    Storage->>Storage: 23. Write blob to container
    Storage-->>Frontend: 24. 201 Created
    
    %% Success Feedback
    Frontend->>User: 25. Show success message
    Frontend->>API: 26. GET /api/list?container=upload
    API->>Storage: 27. listBlobsFlat()
    Storage-->>API: 28. Return blob list
    API-->>Frontend: 29. Return JSON: { "list": [...] }
    Frontend->>User: 30. Display uploaded files
    
    %% Styling
    Note over User,Storage: âœ… Keyless Authentication<br/>âœ… Time-Limited SAS (10 min)<br/>âœ… RBAC-Enforced<br/>âœ… Direct Upload (no proxy)
